title: The Cell Phone Demos by Catnip Tea
description:
Created in 2013 as a musical project to teach herself the basic ideas of music production and electronic sounds, Catnip Tea developed a series of songs titled The Cell Phone Demos. 
In order to reach out to her audience (and because the quality didn't seem fair enough) Catnip Tea released this EP for FREE DOWNLOAD starting in 2014 before it's live release across all other major distributors. To check it out for yourself watch the songs on YouTube, or add them to your Spotify playlists. If you like it, and want to help support the artist, feel free to visit iTunes and buy the EP for less than $5
